A space wallpaper with dynamic shadows and movement.
Press the button to set the wallpaper
Select which planet/moon to use as the foreground
Select the time it will take for the planet to perform one revolution
Enables using hi-resolution textures rather than the standard ones. Will cause frames drops and more memory usage.
The left and right overdraw of animators. Default is 150, increasing it will increase the size of the planets.
The amount to offset the planets relative to the y coordinate. Default is 600, increasing it will shift the planets towards the center.
